des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Opti smart products after connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Opti Kinect” app in the App market then register an account;
(2) Configure your Opti smart products in the Opti Kinect app and enter appropriate names for your devices;
(3) Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from android, iOS or Amazon app market, then configure your Amazon Echo product with the "Alexa" app;
(4) Search for the “Opti Kinect” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable the “Opti Kinect” skill, and you will be navigated to the “Opti Kinect” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete the linking process;
(7) Setup is now complete. You can now enjoy voice control on your Opti smart products using commands like these:
“Alexa, turn on Aura”
“Alexa, turn off Aura”
“Alexa, set Aura brightness to 25 percent”
“Alexa, turn off Aura in 10 minutes”
“Alexa, cancel Aura timer”
